item.description:
Come join us at our Monthly Meet Up and make new friends or just catch up with old ones!


Hi Everybody!

This months meeting will be held at the Met Bar in the Natick Collection once again as we had a very nice turnout the last time we were there.

Please keep in mind that reservations have been made. Therefore, if you RSVP yes and your plans change be sure to update your RSVP ASAP. I look forward to seeong you all there.
item.how_to_find_us: We have reservations in the lounge area under Meetup.
